X Chat Azure
------------

* Preferences -> [Input box ->] uncheck Autocorrection
* Preferences -> Text box -> Colored nick names
* Preferences -> Text box -> Enable time stamps
* Preferences -> User list -> User list sorted by: A-Z
* Preferences -> Channel switch -> Switcher type: Tabs
* Preferences -> Channel switch -> uncheck "Pop new tabs to front"
* Preferences -> Channel switch -> Show channel switcher at: Top
* Preferences -> Events/Sounds
  * Channel Action: Sv
  * Channel Action Hilight: Sv
  * Channel INVITE: Sv
  * Channel Message: Gv Sv
  * Channel Msg Hilight: Gv Sv
  * Private Message: Sv
  * Private Message to Dialog: Sv
  * Topic Change: Gv Sv
* Preferences -> Advanced -> Automatically rejoin channel
